{
  "name": "Locus: Baleful*",
  "type": "equipment",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div><p><em>(Requires attunement by a creature. The properties of this item are affixed to a weapon.)</em></p></div><p><em>This item is a @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.rules.JournalEntry.nniVtdJB1oyk5Sa3]{locus} and can be combined with other <strong>Loci </strong>per the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.rules.JournalEntry.nniVtdJB1oyk5Sa3.JournalEntryPage.zI0VWGKnYZqz6sKd]{Combining Loci} rules.</em></p><p>This preserved, gnarled claw is difficult to distinguish the creature it originates from, but what is clear is that it was not surrendered willingly.</p><p>While attuned the claw merges magically merges with a <strong>weapon</strong> of your choice. This can be done during a short or long rest, requires 10 minutes to complete and it upon completion leaves a visible impression of the claw on the weapon. Once completed, the weapon becomes magical for the purpose of overcoming resistances.</p><p><strong>Effect: </strong>Gain <em>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.magic-items.Item.Mi8FDWw2xKUBau5a]{Baleful Strike}</em></p><p><strong>Special:</strong> When you would regain hit dice, as per completing a long rest, roll a d6 for each hit die expended on <em>Baleful Strike. </em>On a result of 1-3, you do not regain the missing hit die. When you are critically hit, you take additional damage equal to the number of hit dice you failed to regain.</p><blockquote><p><strong>Upon attuning to a weapon with this locus attached, you will need to add the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.magic-items.Item.Mi8FDWw2xKUBau5a]{Baleful Strike} feature to your character sheet manually.</strong></p></blockquote>",
